<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">还</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson9b951e502a99">
<p>子之还兮，遭我乎峱之间兮。并驱从两肩兮，揖我谓我儇兮。<br />子之茂兮，遭我乎峱之道兮。并驱从两牡兮，揖我谓我好兮。<br />子之昌兮，遭我乎峱之阳兮。并驱从两狼兮，揖我谓我臧兮。</p>
</div>
</div>
